                  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="http://www1.uwindsor.ca">Home</a> / <a href="http://www1.uwindsor.ca/graduate">Graduate Studies</a> / <a href="/graduate/faculty-and-staff-resources" class="active">for Faculty and Staff</a></div>                                      <h1 class="title">Resources for Faculty, Staff, and Graduate Administrators</h1>
                                                                                          <div id="node-674" class="node node-type-page"><div class="node-inner">
      <div class="content">
    <h6>
	<strong>Resources for graduate program administrators:</strong></h6>
<ul>
<li>
		Information about upcoming events, current scholarship competitions, etc.&nbsp;will be posted in&nbsp;the &quot;<em>Grad News</em>&quot; section in the right top corner of this&nbsp;website</li>
<li>
		<a href="/grad/system/files/2013 information for graduate programs.pdf">Information&nbsp;manual&nbsp;for new graduate secretaries/program administrators </a><em>(updated June 2013)</em>&nbsp;(pdf).</li>
<li>
		<a href="admissions">Admissions workflow</a> / <a href="admission-tools-0">Admission tools</a>
<ul>
<li>
				<a href="entrance-scholarship-deadlines">entrance scholarship deadlines</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
		<a href="/grad/graduate-faculty">Graduate Faculty designation</a></li>
<li>
		<a href="http://web4.uwindsor.ca/gradcalendar">Graduate Calendar</a>
<ul>
<li>
				<a href="senate-policies-for-graduate-students">Academic Policies and Regulations</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
		<em>(new)</em> <a href="/grad/system/files/Part-time registration regulation.pdf">Regulation re: number of courses allowed for <u>part-time</u> graduate students&nbsp;</a>(for students beginning their graduate program in Fall 2012 or later)</li>
<li>
		<a href="guidelines-for-major-papers-theses-and-dissertations">Thesis Regulations </a>
<ul>
<li>
				<a href="thesis-supervision-guidelines">Research Guidelines&nbsp;</a></li>
<li>
				<a href="external-examiner-for-phd-defenses">External Examiner for PhD dissertations</a></li>
<li>
				<em>(new)</em> Guidelines for conducting Final Oral Defenses: <a href="/grad/system/files/Guidelines%20for%20Conducting%20Oral%20Exams%20for%20Doctoral%20Examining%20Committees.pdf">Doctoral </a>/ <a href="/grad/system/files/Guidelines%20for%20Conducting%20Oral%20Exams%20for%20Masters%20Examining%20Committees.pdf">Master&#39;s</a></li>
<li>
				<em>(new)</em> <a href="http://www1.uwindsor.ca/grad/system/files/Attendance@Defense.pdf">Guidelines for attendance at major paper, thesis, and dissertation&nbsp;defenses</a></li>
<li>
				<a href="/graduate/upcoming-oral-defenses">Upcoming final oral&nbsp;defenses</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
